{
  "stem": "11744.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In every village in France, there is a place where the women come wash-- a wash place-- I don't know how you call that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's where you say that plaque that they put there, the day he was killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they didn't know his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't know who he was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the peasant-- the peasant that night made a casket, and put him in a casket, and buried him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And because some people had made a casket for him, the next day, the Germans came to pick them up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and-- they-- they killed three men-- they killed three men over his tombstone, because they had buried him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so his-- his men arrested a guy in the big city where they had their camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They arrested him, dragged him up there, and they tortured him, and they killed him on my husband's tombstone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, there's been-- you don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was-- this was our life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so when I finally went there-- and I finally was able to go because the Germans finally left France-- I went there-- and I went to the woman where he had-- where all these guys used to spend the night when they went on duty.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She always had rooms for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was told to go and see her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She would take me there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went there, and the first thing she said to me, that you have to recognize him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, no, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I won't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she said, the religion say that you have to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, not my Jewish religion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jews are not-- are not bound to recognize someone who has been so tortured that I would not recognize him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't want that kind of memory in my mind.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
